Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:48.83,ED_S2,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\blur4.5\fad(100,150)}No final, eu só estava satisfazendo meu próprio ego
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:54.17,ED_S2,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\blur4.5\fad(100,150)}E{\3c&H000000&}s{\3c&H000000&}s{\3c&H000000&} é{\3c&H000000&} a{\3c&H000000&} d{\3c&H000000&}o{\3c&H000000&} q{\3c&H000000&}u{\3c&H000000&}e{\3c&H000000&} v{\3c&H000000&}i{\3c&H000000&}m{\3c&H000000&} c{\3c&H000000&}a{\3c&H000000&}r{\3c&H000000&}r{\3c&H000000&}e{\3c&H000000&}g{\3c&H000000&}a{\3c&H000000&}r{\3c&H000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:58.34,ED_S2,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\blur4.5\fad(100,150)}
